00:30:09.060 --> 00:30:10.340
 I'm sorry.

00:30:10.340 --> 00:30:12.500
 Yeah, but you're not wearing anything else.

00:30:12.500 --> 00:30:15.940
 Yeah, okay.

00:30:15.940 --> 00:30:19.700
 I never thought about that as part of my personality.

00:30:19.700 --> 00:30:21.300
 I thought I was still a standoffish now.

00:30:21.300 --> 00:30:22.580
 I say, "Have I ever used my life?"

00:30:22.580 --> 00:30:23.540
 You've suffered a lot.

00:30:23.540 --> 00:30:25.380
 I was living in London, isn't it?

00:30:25.380 --> 00:30:26.020
 Yeah, it is.

00:30:26.020 --> 00:30:27.540
 Like if I lived in Puerto Rico.

